name: Flow of thought
description:
Ideas and thought are floating like clouds

1080 x 1080 mp3 | with sound

Clouds like an ideas can have a different forms and it usually depends on the eye of an observer. The interesting thing that it can interpolate to more sophisticated and deeper things. But for others it can be simplified with the time.
I made this seamless loop to deliver the idea of subjectiveness of our mind process.

2021 Igor Yakunin
